Basketball
organizations: Rutgers, The State University of New Jersey
lead_paragraph: Rick Jackson had 15 points and 11 rebounds for his 11th double-double of the season, and fourth-ranked Syracuse remained undefeated with a 67-52 victory over No. 25 Cincinnati.
